Innate Spellcasting.
The yuan-ti's spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 12). The yuan-ti can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:
} At will: [animal friendship] (snakes only)
} 3/day each: [poison spray], [suggestion]

Magic Resistance.
The yuan-ti has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.

ACTIONS

Multiattack.
The yuan-ti makes two melee attacks.

Scimitar.
*Melee Weapon Attack:* +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. *Hit:* 4 (1d6 + 1) slashing damage.

Shortbow.
*Ranged Weapon Attack:* +3 to hit, range 80/320 ft., one target. *Hit:* 4 (1d6 + 1) piercing damage plus 7 (2d6) poison damage.
